{"tid":1577560,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"30幾年前一個日本人 寫咗一個關於今日香港嘅故事","createTime":"2019-09-17T18:18:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T19:42:03.000Z","uid":249945,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0c04630ce1ba9148d7d09a3859109cf2353a000e","tid":1577560,"uid":249945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T18:18:36.000Z","msg":"條友叫宮崎駿<br />\n<br />\n1.女主角因為知道自己家鄉將會畀壞人利用 寧願念一句咒語 將自己家鄉毀滅 實行終極攬炒<br />\n<br />\n2. 主角一開始想搵著制服嘅軍人幫手但到最後原來  發現 軍人都係仆街<br />\n<br />\n3. 軍人由頭到尾都係畀人利用， 低智商見到金發曬狂 到最後俾人過橋抽板 死嘅死傷既傷<br />\n<br />\n4. 一班被稱為海盜 戴住口罩 嘅人 佢哋用行動證明咗佢哋係 有情有意 為大局著想<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aG06udH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaG06udH.png&h=c66eb51d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/f/f5/Castle_in_the_Sky_%281986%29.png/220px-Castle_in_the_Sky_%281986%29.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fthumb%2Ff%2Ff5%2FCastle_in_the_Sky_%25281986%2529.png%2F220px-Castle_in_the_Sky_%25281986%2529.png&h=c103be26&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f80bb34130c0ace944cdb8e16f6568105d09b73","tid":1577560,"uid":152222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T18:22:41.000Z","msg":"laputa"},{"pid":"b4b22cf338d3c2603a047ea6a01d7003ab59cab0","tid":1577560,"uid":26274,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T18:24:20.000Z","msg":"Sheeta"},{"pid":"a29c7e0d25b539fd0a9377620d9e72d2fecfcab8","tid":1577560,"uid":236359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T18:30:16.000Z","msg":"laputa"},{"pid":"be277575d0b3275d7ad159cbcf7ca402bb34baa6","tid":1577560,"uid":203497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T19:42:03.000Z","msg":"穿鑿附會"}]}